 Includes   company representatives  electric  WiFi  lunch and parking  Payment  Credit card and check payments are accepted for the Career Fair  Please make checks payable to  University of Illinois at Chicago and send to  University of Illinois at Chicago  UIC Engineering Career Center Attn  Rose Coppola Conroy     S  Morgan St  Rm     SEO Chicago  IL       ads Market your company in our career fair booklet  on giant screens within the fair  or within our weekly e newsletter to all UIC engineering and computer science students  You may provide us with an ad that your marketing team creates  or we can create an ad for you Please note the deadline to request company ads is Friday  February  st No refunds for cancelled ads will be provided after Friday  February  st Refund policy  February  th  Refunds will not be processed if any employer does not attend the fair  February  st On Campus Interviews  Due to the high demand for interview room space  cancellations will only be refunded up until Monday  February  th Shipping Any career fair materials may be shipped to  University of Illinois at Chicago  UIC Engineering Career Center Attn  Rose Coppola Conroy     S  Morgan St  Rm     SEO Chicago  IL       Deadline to ship materials  Friday  February  th Return Shipping  Return shipping is provided by FedEx only OCI On campus interviews will be hosted at UIC on Thursday  February    as space allows  We strongly recommend registering for on campus interviews early since space is limited  Interview space is semi private  potentially two or more employers in one room Lunch  parking  wifi  water  and coffee included On campus interview registration is included in the career fair registration form Please note that due to the high demand for interview room space  cancellations for on campus interviews will only be refunded until Monday  February  th  Any employer who cancels on campus interviews after February  th will not be refunded Questions about on campus interviews  Please contact Patrick Devanney at  prd uic edu prd uic edu tips As visitors to the UIC campus  you expected to abide by University policies  including sexual harassment policies Before the Career Fair  post the positions you are recruiting for in UICcareers com After the Career Fair  other ways to engage with UIC students Contact us  n nUIC Logo n n n n UIC Logo  n          Engineering Career Center n         Contact               rcconroy uic edu Social Media Accounts  nTwitter n Twitter UIC edu links UIC edu Academic Calendar Athletics Campus Directory Disability Resources Emergency Information Event Calendar Job Openings Library Maps UIC Today UI Health Veterans Affairs Privacy Statement Campuses University of Illinois System Urbana Champaign Springfield Cookie Settings 